re the advantages of renewable energy read green energy can supply a significant proportion of the country’s energy needs which has many benefits such as environmental improvement an increase of fuel diversity and regional economic development how do i know xoom energy is truly providing renewable energy read xoom energy provides consumers with renewable energy information based on state law and regional fuel mix on our disclosure labels click on your individual renewable plan for more details these disclosure labels are often limited to the system mix and for those enrolled in a renewable energy program they may not include the additional voluntary renewable energy associated with your product why does renewable energy cost more read renewable energy costs more than traditional energy due to limited resources and availability of renewable energy at this time what happens if i move read if you plan to move to an area where xoom energy offers service just contact us at least  days before your move and we will attempt to transfer your service to your new location if xoom energy is unable to transfer the service to your new service address you may cancel your service without penalty who does xoom energy purchase renewable energy from read to offer you competitive rates xoom energy purchases its renewable energy from various energy vendors can a customer switch from a standard product to a renewable energy product read yes customers can switch from a standard variable plan to a fixed renewable product if offered how does xoom energy reduce my energy costs read xoom energy cannot guarantee savings because each of our service plans offers a unique value proposition fixed rate service plans are an excellent way to lock in your rate in for the long haul and avoid price fluctuations your pricing remains steady providing you with consistency and peace of mind variable rate plans are based on market conditions and priced on a monthly basis if youre not looking for a longterm contract and enjoy the flexibility of marketbased rates this is the service plan for you what sets us apart from other energy suppliers read we offer innovative plans at competitive rates combined with excellent customer service we keep it simple and straightforward this all adds up to a great value how does xoom energy provide renewable energy above and beyond what is required by law read xoom energy purchases renewable energy credits recs on behalf of our voluntary green customers an rec represents the property rights to the environmental social and other nonpower qualities of renewable electricity generation recs provide flexibility in procuring green power across a diverse geographical area and applying the renewable attributes to the electricity use at a facility of choice this flexibility allows organizations to support renewable energy development and protect the environment when green power products are not locally available recs can be generated from a variety of renewable sources including but not limited to solar wind and hydro featuredplans variablerate fixedrate renewableenergy comparerates featured plans  saves lives when you enroll on bizrescuelock   of your monthly energy charges will be donated to petsmart charities bizrescuelock  fixed rate  months utility dayton power and light co kwh choose details plan description     get the peace of mind you deserve with our bizrescuelock  fixed rate plan• enroll on bizrescuelock  and  of your monthly energy charges will be donated to petsmart charities• lock in your rate for  full months• get stability for the duration of your term• protect your business from the uncertainty that youve come to expect with energy billsrate above applies to all kwhs usedrate above is only available to new customers enrolling with xoom for the first time additional documents and information cost recovery fee  no monthly fee   terms  conditions pdf contract summary pdf environmental disclosure information pdf things you need to kn